      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative example of precision engineering, maintained to a standard that exceeds factory specifications. This vehicle features a meticulously balanced rotating assembly and a re-mapped ECU that ensures a perfectly linear torque curve. The suspension geometry has been dialed in to eliminate bump steer, while the uprated bushings provide unparalleled road feel without compromising NVH levels. The valvetrain is exceptionally quiet, showing zero signs of eccentric shaft wear, and the compression across all cylinders remains within 2% of factory fresh. Finished with a multi-stage paint correction and a high-solids ceramic coating, the aesthetic matches the mechanical integrity. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the driver who demands peak performance and structural rigidity.",
